{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2020/02/04/用Powershell更新Windows.html","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"宫不上叔"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"645bec7b-385e-5161-b267-d2fa88290334","excerpt":"用Powershell更新Windows 发现已经半个月没有被Windows更新打扰了，原来是一个累积更新挂了，我发现在图形界面下面怎么更新都失败，于是寻思在命令行执行。 在powershell中有一个包PSUpdateWindows可以派上用场。","html":"<h1>用Powershell更新Windows</h1>\n<p>发现已经半个月没有被Windows更新打扰了，原来是一个累积更新挂了，我发现在图形界面下面怎么更新都失败，于是寻思在命令行执行。</p>\n<p>在powershell中有一个包PSUpdateWindows可以派上用场。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-powershell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-powershell\">Install<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Module PSUpdateWindow\n\nGet<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>WindowsUpdate <span class=\"token comment\">#下载更新</span>\n\nInstall<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>WindowsUpdate <span class=\"token comment\">#安装更新</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/02/04/用Powershell更新Windows.html","date":"February 04, 2020","title":"用Powershell更新Windows"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2020/02/04/用Powershell更新Windows.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/plan/2020/02/01/一月总结和二月计划.html","title":"一月总结和二月计划"},"frontmatter":{"category":"plan"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/02/04/Windows上使用scrapy爬网页.html","title":"Windows上使用scrapy爬网页"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}}}}}